WEBVTT

1
00:02:39.492 --> 00:02:43.485
Our lndia is the best..

2
00:02:43.897 --> 00:02:47.993
of all the world by far

3
00:02:48.234 --> 00:02:52.170
Our lndia is the best..

4
00:02:52.572 --> 00:02:56.668
..of all the world by far

5
00:02:57.076 --> 00:03:00.773
We are it's buds.

6
00:03:01.347 --> 00:03:05.443
lt is our garden. all ours. ours.

7
00:03:05.718 --> 00:03:09.484
Our lndia is the best..

8
00:03:10.056 --> 00:03:12.490
..of all the world by far

9
00:03:12.725 --> 00:03:13.487
This way.

10
00:03:24.737 --> 00:03:26.830
Our tomorrow is based on our today

11
00:03:27.607 --> 00:03:29.336
What we choose to do today will decide..

12
00:03:29.909 --> 00:03:31.740
..what happens to us tomorrow.

13
00:03:32.078 --> 00:03:34.171
The choice isn't between good and evil.

14
00:03:34.581 --> 00:03:35.513
That's easy.

15
00:03:36.449 --> 00:03:39.179
The real choices of life
are choosing between..

16
00:03:39.953 --> 00:03:45.220
..the lesser of two evils.
or the greater of two goods.

17
00:03:46.459 --> 00:03:49.155
Now what do you choose.
Zooni. what's your choice?

18
00:03:50.630 --> 00:03:52.461
Oh. leave my little girl alone!

19
00:03:53.466 --> 00:03:55.991
Just listen to your heart dear..

20
00:03:56.236 --> 00:03:57.567
..not your father's philosophy!

21
00:03:58.037 --> 00:04:00.164
Try and take some decisions..

22
00:04:00.340 --> 00:04:02.171
..from the heart rather than the brain. Zulfi

23
00:04:03.076 --> 00:04:08.013
lf l'd used my brain you wouldn't be here.
Nafisa my love.

24
00:04:10.149 --> 00:04:10.945
So? Zooni?

25
00:04:11.951 --> 00:04:15.785
Papa. Mama. l really can't decide.

26
00:04:16.389 --> 00:04:19.051
l'll do whatever you say.

27
00:04:23.463 --> 00:04:25.454
So that's it. lt's decided.

28
00:04:25.798 --> 00:04:27.561
Zooni will not go to Delhi.

29
00:04:31.638 --> 00:04:36.575
l found my prince.
When will Zooni find hers?

30
00:04:37.810 --> 00:04:41.473
When will some footballer
hit her head with a ball?

31
00:04:42.248 --> 00:04:43.237
Any regrets?

32
00:04:43.483 --> 00:04:44.643
Regrets?

33
00:04:45.351 --> 00:04:51.347
l praise God every day that the
great Zulfikar Ali Beg's..

34
00:04:52.025 --> 00:04:52.855
..penalty kick missed the goal..

35
00:04:53.192 --> 00:04:54.625
..and hit me. square on the head.

36
00:04:54.861 --> 00:04:57.455
lt was my worst kick ever!

37
00:04:57.697 --> 00:04:58.721
Any regrets?

38
00:04:59.132 --> 00:04:59.962
Regrets?

39
00:05:00.967 --> 00:05:04.733
That's why l tended to you
in the hospital for a week.

40
00:05:08.374 --> 00:05:10.740
We must accept that Zooni..

41
00:05:11.477 --> 00:05:14.173
..may have to live her life without
that special someone.

42
00:05:14.447 --> 00:05:17.245
That perhaps she will never marry.

43
00:05:18.985 --> 00:05:24.548
And when we're gone
who will look out for her?

44
00:05:25.358 --> 00:05:27.451
We must give her the
chance to live her life.

45
00:05:28.494 --> 00:05:32.294
We need to support her independence.

46
00:05:32.932 --> 00:05:37.096
Be her strength. not her weakness.

47
00:05:57.357 --> 00:05:58.585
Madam Mehbooba

48
00:05:59.025 --> 00:06:01.619
Bobo. the name is Bobo not Mehbooba

49
00:06:01.861 --> 00:06:03.294
Whatever you command your highness.

50
00:06:03.529 --> 00:06:06.123
By the way. your bags weigh
more than your brain!

51
00:06:06.532 --> 00:06:09.126
Obviously! Haven't you heard that saying?

52
00:06:09.369 --> 00:06:11.860
Which one?
- ''The buffalo is bigger than the brain.''

53
00:06:12.205 --> 00:06:14.298
No dummy. it's ''ls the brain bigger
or the buffalo?''

54
00:06:14.540 --> 00:06:16.474
Fatty! - Not Fatty. Fatima.

55
00:06:16.709 --> 00:06:19.075
Don't know why you girls insist on
distorting perfectly good names.

56
00:06:19.312 --> 00:06:22.213
Yes. Ruby. - Not Ruby. Rubina.

57
00:06:23.116 --> 00:06:24.549
Come on.. take the bags at least!

58
00:06:32.024 --> 00:06:34.492
We have to represent Kashmir.
at a Republic Day performance..

59
00:06:34.761 --> 00:06:37.025
..at the President's Palace.
in front of the Chief Minister of Delhi..

60
00:06:37.263 --> 00:06:39.356
..and what do l have to pull this off?

61
00:06:39.599 --> 00:06:42.693
A bunch of wild cats!

62
00:06:43.369 --> 00:06:46.270
lf we're a bunch of wild cats
what does that make our leader?

63
00:06:48.808 --> 00:06:49.536
Who said that?

64
00:06:49.776 --> 00:06:51.539
You've carried your knitting?

65
00:06:53.279 --> 00:06:56.146
When we're upset.
we say things to distract

66
00:06:56.382 --> 00:06:57.212
''Have you taken your knitting?

67
00:06:57.450 --> 00:06:58.644
Kept your ticket safely?

68
00:06:59.252 --> 00:07:00.310
Don't get off at a station on the way.''

69
00:07:00.586 --> 00:07:01.814
God keep you safe.

70
00:07:02.088 --> 00:07:09.460
Papa.. papa! When papa's upset.
not just his voice

71
00:07:09.695 --> 00:07:11.026
His walk also changes.

72
00:07:11.264 --> 00:07:15.530
Yes. and he can't even cry in front of all these girls.

73
00:07:17.003 --> 00:07:19.938
But l have no such problem!

74
00:07:23.209 --> 00:07:28.044
l know you have to do this..

75
00:07:29.215 --> 00:07:31.706
..but l don't know why. l'm afraid.

76
00:07:31.984 --> 00:07:32.951
Afraid of what ?

77
00:07:33.319 --> 00:07:35.048
Loosing me to some prince?

78
00:07:35.321 --> 00:07:35.753
Oh. l wish!

79
00:07:35.988 --> 00:07:38.422
One look at you.
and he'll be on his knees

80
00:07:38.658 --> 00:07:39.920
Heaven forbid! Will he be a porter?

81
00:07:40.159 --> 00:07:41.649
Kneel to get my bags? - Hush!

82
00:07:41.994 --> 00:07:45.430
Not a porter. not your bags.
he'll take your heart away.

83
00:07:46.065 --> 00:07:47.999
With some poetry maybe..

84
00:07:48.401 --> 00:07:51.268
..''Every once in a while
l get this feeling in my heart..

85
00:07:51.671 --> 00:07:54.834
..that you were made for me. all apart.''

86
00:07:55.074 --> 00:07:56.769
''You were living in the
mountains somewhere..

87
00:07:57.009 --> 00:07:58.271
..before there was me.''

88
00:07:59.078 --> 00:08:02.878
''You have been called down
to this earth. only for me.''

89
00:08:10.223 --> 00:08:11.918
God keep you safe. my child.
God keep you safe!

90
00:08:12.158 --> 00:08:13.090
God keep you. mama.

91
00:08:14.060 --> 00:08:16.756
Have a safe journey.

92
00:08:17.330 --> 00:08:20.265
Be sure to say a prayer for me
at the Jama Masjid. - Yes. mama.

93
00:08:20.500 --> 00:08:21.933
Take Zooni for an eye test in the big city..

94
00:08:22.168 --> 00:08:23.863
..and you. Rubina take care of my baby!

95
00:08:24.103 --> 00:08:25.263
Relax Aunty.

96
00:08:25.505 --> 00:08:27.097
Don't worry. l'm here aren't l?

97
00:08:27.340 --> 00:08:28.773
That's what l'm afraid of Fatima.

98
00:08:29.008 --> 00:08:30.100
lt's Fatty. aunty.

99
00:08:30.776 --> 00:08:32.437
Bye dear. Bye Zooni!

100
00:08:37.183 --> 00:08:39.515
Mama! Mama!

101
00:08:39.886 --> 00:08:40.318
Yes.my child !

102
00:08:40.820 --> 00:08:43.448
lf the Prince recites poetry
what should l say?

103
00:08:45.057 --> 00:08:47.992
''May my life's breath find refuge in your heart..

104
00:08:48.561 --> 00:08:51.826
..destroyed in your love may my life depart.''

105
00:08:54.100 --> 00:08:55.499
Bye Mama!

106
00:09:22.895 --> 00:09:25.159
Why do you do this?

107
00:09:26.799 --> 00:09:28.596
You can say something as well.

108
00:09:28.834 --> 00:09:30.995
Now listen up Rao.
We're here for just 7 days.

109
00:09:31.237 --> 00:09:33.501
5 days to the show. and 2 for holidaying.

110
00:09:33.739 --> 00:09:37.675
l want to sight- see Delhi.
not your bald head.

111
00:09:37.910 --> 00:09:38.740
Stand straight like a man!

112
00:09:39.078 --> 00:09:40.170
l'm not even a man any more Madam.

113
00:09:40.413 --> 00:09:42.608
After years of bowing to
government officers..

114
00:09:42.848 --> 00:09:44.179
..l have come to this sorry state.

115
00:09:44.417 --> 00:09:47.011
Today if l have children.
even they will be born bent over.

116
00:09:48.788 --> 00:09:50.756
l have no interest in your
family planning program!

117
00:09:51.023 --> 00:09:51.955
Where is that tour guide?

118
00:10:01.133 --> 00:10:04.625
l am the Balwaan.
Not the Cartoon Network.

119
00:10:04.870 --> 00:10:06.337
You are exactly what you look like!

120
00:10:06.639 --> 00:10:07.799
Now tell me what's the problem here?

121
00:10:08.808 --> 00:10:10.070
Where do l start?

122
00:10:10.409 --> 00:10:11.398
From the head light to the exhaust..

123
00:10:11.644 --> 00:10:13.475
..there are problems and more problems.

124
00:10:18.184 --> 00:10:20.846
l mean your tour guide.
Where on earth is he?

125
00:10:21.287 --> 00:10:28.625
''Don't look around the city
Forget the wasteland too''

126
00:10:29.195 --> 00:10:34.792
''Behold God's greatest creation.
Rehan is just above you.''

127
00:10:47.046 --> 00:10:49.640
You Mr. Romeo. Stop this cheap poetry!

128
00:10:56.155 --> 00:10:58.453
You didn't applaud me. now atleast help me

129
00:11:00.359 --> 00:11:01.348
Oh. you're blind.

130
00:11:01.594 --> 00:11:04.392
Yes. you didn't see that?
Are you blind too?

131
00:11:07.033 --> 00:11:09.194
Thank God. l'm not.

132
00:11:10.536 --> 00:11:12.470
That's a nice thing to say to a blind person.

133
00:11:13.205 --> 00:11:14.502
lf l was blind. l couldn't have seen..

134
00:11:14.874 --> 00:11:19.140
..the most beautiful thing in the world. you.

135
00:11:22.214 --> 00:11:27.709
''Your beauty made God make a mistake.
what more can i say ?.

136
00:11:27.987 --> 00:11:30.512
So that you don't caste an evil eye on yourself.
he took your eyes away.''

137
00:11:33.592 --> 00:11:34.854
Zooni. where are you?

138
00:11:35.261 --> 00:11:36.023
l'm coming Fatty.

139
00:11:37.263 --> 00:11:39.094
Fatty? ls that your name or your dog's?

140
00:11:41.367 --> 00:11:42.026
Come on Balwante..

141
00:11:42.268 --> 00:11:44.031
..hit the gas!

142
00:12:14.433 --> 00:12:15.695
Heavenly!

143
00:12:26.212 --> 00:12:27.941
lf wish l was a roll of wool..

144
00:12:30.716 --> 00:12:32.547
lf wish l was a roll of wool..

145
00:12:33.486 --> 00:12:34.919
..wrapped around her fingers..

146
00:12:38.357 --> 00:12:40.757
lf you were a roll of wool.
with the needles.. l'd..

147
00:12:40.993 --> 00:12:44.929
l wish she'd make a sweater out of me.
wear me. even in the summer.

148
00:12:46.332 --> 00:12:47.594
Wow! What a thought!

149
00:12:50.836 --> 00:12:52.929
Zooni. stop encouraging his nonsense.

150
00:12:54.006 --> 00:12:56.873
''l am not the flowerjasmine.
l am the flower rose.

151
00:13:02.448 --> 00:13:06.009
l am your lifelong admirer.
not of your friend sitting close.''

152
00:13:09.321 --> 00:13:12.813
Hey Mr. Guide. your cheap poetry
is going to get you nowhere.

153
00:13:13.692 --> 00:13:15.250
So. who are you knitting this sweater for?

154
00:13:15.494 --> 00:13:19.089
She's knitting it for a prince.
not for a devil like you.

155
00:13:19.331 --> 00:13:21.595
And if she was interested in you ..

156
00:13:21.834 --> 00:13:22.926
..she would speak up not sit silent.

157
00:13:23.169 --> 00:13:24.329
Oh. so she does speak ?

158
00:13:25.004 --> 00:13:26.835
l knew she was blind.
thought she was mute too

159
00:13:28.474 --> 00:13:32.342
Zooni! Don't talk to him.
You don't know these men..

160
00:13:32.912 --> 00:13:34.436
Looks like you know men very well.

161
00:13:35.514 --> 00:13:36.344
Stupid guide

162
00:13:40.452 --> 00:13:44.718
''lf you sit there in silence. regret it you will.

163
00:13:45.891 --> 00:13:49.292
So often after silence love
has awakened. stronger still.''

164
00:13:58.237 --> 00:14:00.603
''There is no limit to human desire..''

165
00:14:01.507 --> 00:14:04.101
''There is no limit to human desire. no dearth.

166
00:14:05.110 --> 00:14:08.273
After 2 yards of burial cloth.
we still want 2 yards of earth.''

167
00:14:08.514 --> 00:14:09.276
Superb!

168
00:14:09.582 --> 00:14:12.107
Superb! Outstanding!

169
00:14:15.888 --> 00:14:20.154
''l'll look pain square in the eye.
face every test laid out for me.

170
00:14:20.759 --> 00:14:25.662
For the sake of your friendship.
dear friend. l'll even love my enemy.''

171
00:14:31.403 --> 00:14:33.667
Oh yeah. l love your style!

172
00:14:36.075 --> 00:14:38.509
The emperor Shah Jahan once walked
these lanes of the Red Fort.

173
00:14:39.845 --> 00:14:47.752
And so did Mumtaz.
his very. very beautiful wife.- Careful!

174
00:14:50.289 --> 00:14:51.221
l can manage myself.

175
00:14:51.457 --> 00:14:53.118
But how will l manage myself. around you.

176
00:14:59.298 --> 00:15:00.060
Shall we?

177
00:15:06.739 --> 00:15:08.331
Bobo. tell me. what does he look like?

178
00:15:08.574 --> 00:15:12.840
Killer. girl. a real killer.

179
00:15:26.325 --> 00:15:27.519
He's simply obnoxious!

180
00:15:27.960 --> 00:15:31.054
He looks ok. so l thought
he must be a nice guy..

181
00:15:31.297 --> 00:15:33.322
..but he called me a stupid girl.. so..

182
00:15:34.199 --> 00:15:35.894
And forget all his sweet talk..

183
00:15:36.235 --> 00:15:38.396
.. the way he looks at women.its shameful!

184
00:15:38.637 --> 00:15:40.696
And he told me he doesn't believe in God.
can you imagine that?

185
00:15:42.708 --> 00:15:44.232
Look even the crows are cawing.
lt's a sign.

186
00:15:44.476 --> 00:15:46.000
Stay away from that Rehan guide.

187
00:15:46.478 --> 00:15:48.912
''How can you stay away from me and go?

188
00:15:50.249 --> 00:15:53.412
How can your heart forget me so?

189
00:15:54.253 --> 00:15:56.813
That fragrance on your breath is me.

190
00:15:57.890 --> 00:16:00.791
How ever will you stop. not breathe?''

191
00:16:04.463 --> 00:16:05.395
Great! Fabulous!

192
00:16:05.631 --> 00:16:06.563
Come on. let's go.

193
00:16:06.799 --> 00:16:07.390
Come.

194
00:17:03.922 --> 00:17:07.619
lf the moon was to recommend me.

195
00:17:07.860 --> 00:17:10.795
This is what he'd say to you.

196
00:17:11.630 --> 00:17:15.464
l want to drop the veil of decency.

197
00:17:15.701 --> 00:17:18.636
l want to cross the line with you.

198
00:17:19.538 --> 00:17:23.304
l insist on destroying myself.

199
00:17:23.542 --> 00:17:27.137
On destroying myself in you.

200
00:17:27.479 --> 00:17:31.142
lf the moon was to recommend me.

201
00:17:31.383 --> 00:17:34.352
This is what he'd say to you.

202
00:17:35.254 --> 00:17:39.020
l want to drop the veil of decency.

203
00:17:39.324 --> 00:17:42.521
l want to cross the line with you.

204
00:18:06.652 --> 00:18:10.520
Your charms are like a gentle breeze.

205
00:18:10.756 --> 00:18:13.520
Let them touch me as you pass.

206
00:18:14.593 --> 00:18:18.256
Your every move a graceful branch.

207
00:18:18.530 --> 00:18:21.465
Please move into my heart.

208
00:18:22.601 --> 00:18:26.367
Come into my arms.
any excuse will do.

209
00:18:26.605 --> 00:18:30.200
For l must. l must destroy myself in you.

210
00:18:30.442 --> 00:18:34.208
lf the moon was to recommend me.

211
00:18:34.446 --> 00:18:37.381
This is what he'd say to you.

212
00:18:38.283 --> 00:18:42.185
l want to drop the veil of decency.

213
00:18:42.421 --> 00:18:45.879
l want to cross the line with you.

214
00:19:29.401 --> 00:19:33.098
lf l tell you my true intentions.

215
00:19:33.338 --> 00:19:36.330
l'm sure they'll make you blush.

216
00:19:37.176 --> 00:19:41.112
lf l make you hear my heartbeats.

217
00:19:41.346 --> 00:19:44.281
l'm sure they'll leave you flushed.

218
00:19:45.384 --> 00:19:48.945
But l cannot hide my feelings true.

219
00:19:49.221 --> 00:19:52.987
For l must. l must destroy myself in you.

220
00:19:53.225 --> 00:19:56.922
lf the moon was to recommend me.

221
00:19:57.162 --> 00:20:00.154
This is what he'd say to you.

222
00:20:01.066 --> 00:20:04.661
l want to drop the veil of decency.

223
00:20:05.070 --> 00:20:08.005
l want to cross the line with you.

224
00:20:08.974 --> 00:20:12.603
l insist on destroying myself.

225
00:20:12.844 --> 00:20:17.679
On destroying myself in you.

226
00:20:38.303 --> 00:20:42.399
Stand straight. Looking at you
l'm getting a backache.

227
00:20:42.641 --> 00:20:44.575
And you Mr. Cartoon Network..

228
00:20:44.810 --> 00:20:47.074
..we have to leave for rehearsal
at exactly 9 AM tomorrow.

229
00:20:47.312 --> 00:20:48.074
So then leave.

230
00:20:54.019 --> 00:20:55.577
lt's me. Rehan.

231
00:20:57.689 --> 00:21:01.523
l know. Only you can be so impudent.

232
00:21:03.295 --> 00:21:05.229
l want to be even more impudent.

233
00:21:09.301 --> 00:21:11.064
l want you to run away with me.

234
00:21:14.473 --> 00:21:16.407
l want to show you Delhi.

235
00:21:17.342 --> 00:21:26.740
Without your bodyguards.
don't say no. not without thinking atleast

236
00:21:28.520 --> 00:21:31.284
You'll anyway be thinking about me so...

237
00:21:34.860 --> 00:21:36.953
God forbid. the crows are cawing.

238
00:21:42.934 --> 00:21:47.462
l'll wait for you after the rehearsal tomorrow.
With these crows.

239
00:21:56.381 --> 00:22:00.408
You have had more girls in your life
than there is mileage on my bus.

240
00:22:00.852 --> 00:22:03.116
Why do you want this blind girl?

241
00:22:05.190 --> 00:22:09.092
What can l do Balwante.
everyone wants the moon.

242
00:22:09.361 --> 00:22:13.297
There's just one headlight in the sky.
that shows us the way.

243
00:22:13.532 --> 00:22:14.965
Now you want that too?

244
00:22:17.035 --> 00:22:18.969
''They say in love you always loose sleep.

245
00:22:20.372 --> 00:22:26.311
l wish someone would love me.
l bloody sleep and sleep and sleep.''

246
00:22:28.046 --> 00:22:28.808
Let's go.

247
00:22:33.752 --> 00:22:36.812
Zooni! You must be tired. go to sleep.

248
00:22:39.257 --> 00:22:40.690
l am awake after so many years.

249
00:22:42.260 --> 00:22:47.698
l can't sleep now. l can't sleep now.

250
00:22:54.005 --> 00:22:58.203
l want to be even more impudent.
l want you to run away with me.

251
00:22:59.277 --> 00:23:00.642
Why aren't you concentrating?

252
00:23:01.213 --> 00:23:02.646
Can l use your phone ?

253
00:23:09.588 --> 00:23:10.646
Pick up. mama!

254
