people all day long!

311
00:27:17.535 --> 00:27:20.060
l can't see Rehan today.

312
00:27:20.672 --> 00:27:21.900
l can't see him either.

313
00:27:24.342 --> 00:27:29.245
l think he's like me.
Completely clean at heart..

314
00:27:29.481 --> 00:27:32.075
