but his state was such that l could not.

746
01:11:17.373 --> 01:11:19.807
So you have to identify him. Zooni.
ls this Rehan?

747
01:11:23.245 --> 01:11:28.080
No! lt can't be Rehan. lt can't!

748
01:11:28.317 --> 01:11:33.516
Please. don't make my daughter
go through this. Please.

749
01:11:37.459 --> 01:11:38.721
lt's compulsory.

750
01:11:49.371 --> 01:11:53.637
Zooni my darling. even this is life.

751
01:12:01.850 --> 01:12:03.841
lf only l was a roll of wool

752
01:12:04.520 --> 01:12:06.078
wrapped around her fingers..

753
01:12:17.132 --> 01:12:19.794
That fragrance on your breath is me.

754
01:12:20.903 --> 01:12:23.963
How ever will you stop. not breathe?

755
01:12:27.543 --> 01:12:32.810
How can you love me so much?
How can anyone love another so much?

756
01:12:38.921 --> 01:12:42.413
Don't come close to me.
this storm will destroy you.

757
01:12:52.101 --> 01:12:56.037
Think about it. if l go today
l won't come back tomorrow.

758
01:13:04.880 --> 01:13:07.314
At this time we are at the
Bureau of Military lntelligence.

759
01:13:07.549 --> 01:13:10.518
There is not much information
forthcoming on the blast..

760
01:13:10.753 --> 01:13:13.688
..but here is the head of the
Anti-Terrorist Unit.

761
01:13:13.922 --> 01:13:17.585
Mr. Susheel Rawat. Mr. Rawat.
What can you tell us about the blast?

762
01:13:18.961 --> 01:13:21.191
When we know more.
We'll tell you more.

763
01:13:21.430 --> 01:13:25.025
But something to go on.
who is responsible.

764
01:13:25.434 --> 01:13:26.196
These media people.

765
01:13:26.435 --> 01:13:29.199
They start 24 hour channels
and then get after us to fill the time.

766
01:13:30.105 --> 01:13:31.197
Everything is under control.

767
01:13:31.673 --> 01:13:34.471
Sir. Tyagi has been called from
intelligence agency RAW

768
01:13:35.544 --> 01:13:39.605
Tyagi? Now things will be out of control.

769
01:13:43.385 --> 01:13:45.945
So Tyagi. case solved yet?

770
01:13:51.326 --> 01:13:55.422
So what does your psychology
mumbo-jumbo say?

771
01:13:57.666 --> 01:13:58.758
This is his work.

772
01:13:59.001 --> 01:14:01.367
Who? Who are you talking about?

773
01:14:02.771 --> 01:14:04.033
These two are telling the truth.

774
01:14:04.440 --> 01:14:08.706
They haven't seen him.
They were simply given instructions.

775
01:14:09.945 --> 01:14:12.277
The master planner is someone else.

776
01:14:12.781 --> 01:14:15.807
Do you need an invitation
to tell me his name? Who is it?

777
01:14:18.921 --> 01:14:21.321
This man has changed the face of the lKF.

778
01:14:22.658 --> 01:14:28.096
He has taken a rag-tag group
and made it a professional organization.

779
01:14:28.764 --> 01:14:30.925
A group on par with the most
deadly in the world.

780
01:14:31.500 --> 01:14:37.996
On par with the best
intelligence agencies in the world.

781
01:14:38.841 --> 01:14:40.604
lt's because of this man that 8 ships and..

782
01:14:40.843 --> 01:14:44.210
..a large part of the Bombay port
are under water.

783
01:14:44.847 --> 01:14:47.338
lt's because of this man
that lslamabad airport's..

784
01:14:47.683 --> 01:14:49.378
.. new wing was destroyed even
before it could be completed.

785
01:14:51.320 --> 01:14:55.051
He has changed the face of terrorism
in lndia and Pakistan

786
01:14:59.828 --> 01:15:01.591
Those blood shot eyes and..

787
01:15:02.164 --> 01:15:04.428
.. fanatical terrorists are a thing of the past.

788
01:15:05.000 --> 01:15:09.266
This man is a thinker. A planner.
No one knows his name.

789
01:15:09.505 --> 01:15:15.603
No one knows his past.
or where he comes from.

790
01:15:16.011 --> 01:15:17.103
He can be anyone.

791
01:15:17.346 --> 01:15:20.315
The man sitting next to you on the train..

792
01:15:20.682 --> 01:15:24.277
..or a bank teller. or even the
cigarette seller outside.

793
01:15:24.720 --> 01:15:30.317
He is intelligent and he's dangerous.
and he can be anyone.

794
01:15:30.726 --> 01:15:32.660
We have to find him.

795
01:15:32.895 --> 01:15:36.991
For if we don't. he can take
terrorism to a level beyond..

796
01:15:37.399 --> 01:15:39.833
..our imagination because our
imagination is be nothing like his.

797
01:16:31.720 --> 01:16:33.847
l'm sorry Grandfather. the mission
was not entirely successful.

798
01:16:35.557 --> 01:16:36.387
l had set everything.

799
01:16:36.625 --> 01:16:38.217
Those fools just didn't follow instructions.

800
01:16:38.627 --> 01:16:42.393
Not everyone can be like my grandson.
A perfect soldier.

801
01:16:43.832 --> 01:16:49.896
But even he slipped this once.
That too for some woman.

802
01:16:50.973 --> 01:16:53.737
lt's very unusual that
you were carried away like this.

803
01:16:54.309 --> 01:16:55.901
And the woman what about her?

804
01:16:56.144 --> 01:16:56.906
She is with God.

805
01:16:59.514 --> 01:17:00.674
Now listen to me.

806
01:17:00.916 --> 01:17:03.180
You don't have to worry about this soldier sir.

807
01:17:03.552 --> 01:17:04.985
My concentration was. is..

808
01:17:05.721 --> 01:17:06.983
..and will always remain
on our independence.

809
01:17:08.490 --> 01:17:09.923
l am a soldier and nothing else.

810
01:17:10.626 --> 01:17:12.890
That's all l wanted to hear my son.

811
01:17:13.128 --> 01:17:16.996
Now l'll meet you after the Bangkok operation.
May God keep you.

812
01:17:28.076 --> 01:17:30.237
You had taken me to my goal. Zooni.

813
01:17:31.146 --> 01:17:37.085
should never have taken you off that train.
But l became weak.

814
01:17:37.619 --> 01:17:39.086
And l fell in love with you.

815
01:17:41.690 --> 01:17:43.385
l hope you can forgive me.

816
01:17:44.793 --> 01:17:47.455
l should never have brought you
into my life. Never.

817
01:18:02.144 --> 01:18:03.475
God be with you. Zooni.

818
01:18:29.071 --> 01:18:30.060
You are the Defence Secretary.

819
01:18:30.238 --> 01:18:33.435
Do something.
Get that Tyagi off my back!

820
01:18:33.709 --> 01:18:35.643
Last year the Al-Qaeda's attempt
on Delhi airport ..

821
01:18:35.877 --> 01:18:37.640
..was foiled by Tyagi.

822
01:18:38.113 --> 01:18:39.137
She got lucky. once.

823
01:18:39.381 --> 01:18:40.973
And now she thinks she's a
big shot intelligence officer.

824
01:18:41.216 --> 01:18:42.808
l can't do anything now.

825
01:18:43.085 --> 01:18:46.145
The Defence Minister himself
has asked her to be on this case.

826
01:18:46.688 --> 01:18:48.656
Sir. it's nothing less than the Armageddon.

827
01:18:49.591 --> 01:18:52.185
The press shouldn't even get a whiff of this.

828
01:18:52.494 --> 01:18:55.088
This lKF has made our life hell.

829
01:18:55.931 --> 01:18:57.296
First the President Palace bombing..

830
01:18:57.866 --> 01:19:00.460
..then Karachi Oil refinery
and last year it was the..

831
01:19:00.702 --> 01:19:03.136
..plane hijacking. And now we hear
they've stolen parts from us.

832
01:19:03.605 --> 01:19:13.378
Pakistan and Russia and are ready
with a nuclear missile!

833
01:19:14.950 --> 01:19:17.214
Sir. This is their way of forcing lndia
out of Kashmir.

834
01:19:17.619 --> 01:19:18.916
When Kashmir's ruler. Hari Singh.
decided to join lndia..

835
01:19:19.254 --> 01:19:23.156
..in 1947. then why this talk of
independence now?

836
01:19:23.425 --> 01:19:25.518
But the Kashmiri's had also been
promised a vote.

837
01:19:26.194 --> 01:19:30.688
a referendum to decide
whether they wanted to stay a..

838
01:19:30.932 --> 01:19:33.423
..part of lndia. join Pakistan
or then be independent.

839
01:19:33.668 --> 01:19:37.468
All these years later they are
still to get that referendum.

840
01:19:37.706 --> 01:19:39.196
What referendum are you talking about?

841
01:19:39.541 --> 01:19:44.308
When half of Kashmir is occupied
by Pakistan. how is it possible?

842
01:19:44.613 --> 01:19:45.773
A referendum needs
to include all of Kashmir.

843
01:19:46.014 --> 01:19:47.879
why should it include only half?

844
01:19:49.484 --> 01:19:51.543
This is not an lndia-Pakistan
issue any more.

845
01:19:52.387 --> 01:19:55.584
lKF wants both lndia and Pakistan
to leave Kashmir.

846
01:19:56.158 --> 01:19:59.093
They want a separate country.
An independent Kashmir.

847
01:19:59.327 --> 01:20:03.764
Please. l know the history
of lndia and Pakistan.

848
01:20:03.999 --> 01:20:05.762
Tell me about this bomb.

849
01:20:06.001 --> 01:20:09.767
How powerful is this bomb.
Mrs. Tyagi. and what are the dangers?

850
01:20:10.071 --> 01:20:12.972
ln the last few years over 15.000 people
have been killed in Mumbai.

851
01:20:13.208 --> 01:20:19.977
Oklahoma City. New York. Bali.
Madrid and London.

852
01:20:20.382 --> 01:20:22.441
And losses have run into millions.

853
01:20:23.051 --> 01:20:24.484
But if they use this bomb

854
01:20:24.986 --> 01:20:32.256
5 million people can die.
An entire city can be destroyed.

855
01:20:32.894 --> 01:20:35.488
That city can also be our capital. New Delhi.

856
01:20:37.232 --> 01:20:39.666
We must stop this bomb.
Whatever it takes.

857
01:20:40.836 --> 01:20:43.168
But Sir. this bomb is useless for them.

858
01:20:44.072 --> 01:20:44.834
What do you mean?

859
01:20:45.073 --> 01:20:47.405
The missile needs a special.
lndian made trigger.

860
01:20:47.776 --> 01:20:51.678
lf they don't have that.
they can't use the bomb

861
01:20:53.315 --> 01:20:56.682
Only until they get the trigger.
Only until then.

862
01:20:57.786 --> 01:21:00.448
Sir. there's nothing to worry about.
Outside of Delhi.

863
01:21:00.722 --> 01:21:03.691
We have 6 triggers at various
military bases around the country.

864
01:21:04.226 --> 01:21:05.659
ln Rajasthan. Kutch. Darjeeling.

865
01:21:05.894 --> 01:21:08.658
Amritsar. Leh and Kashmir.
They are safe there.

866
01:21:08.897 --> 01:21:10.831
l want all the triggers brought to Delhi.

867
01:21:11.099 --> 01:21:14.500
ln the next 12 hours they will all be here. Sir.

868
01:21:15.136 --> 01:21:17.661
Get me the Defence Minister of Pakistan.

869
01:21:18.106 --> 01:21:20.006
..l want to share this information with him.

870
01:21:21.042 --> 01:21:23.101
We can be sure. Just as we are
taking steps to secure the triggers.

871
01:21:23.378 --> 01:21:26.609
lKF's mastermind will be
taking steps to steal them.

872
01:22:11.793 --> 01:22:13.727
And l will bring this trigger to you myself.

873
01:22:13.962 --> 01:22:16.829
Be alert. lKF will be after you at every step.

874
01:22:17.065 --> 01:22:18.396
lf the weather holds up.
the trigger will be..

875
01:22:18.633 --> 01:22:21.727
..with you in 3 hours. Sir.
Glory to lndia!

876
01:22:21.903 --> 01:22:22.733
Glory to lndia!

877
01:22:24.105 --> 01:22:26.733
This is the day every soldier lives for.

878
01:22:26.908 --> 01:22:28.773
For a chance to serve his country.

879
01:22:29.044 --> 01:22:31.604
The last time you saved me from the lKF.

880
01:22:31.846 --> 01:22:34.679
Today we both must save the
country from the lKF.

881
01:22:38.620 --> 01:22:41.248
This soldier is ready to take
lives or to give his own life.

882
01:22:41.456 --> 01:22:42.889
Anything for his motherland. Sir.

883
01:22:49.698 --> 01:22:59.903
Good news. The trigger will be
with us soon. God keep Rehan!

884
01:23:00.141 --> 01:23:01.972
God is great!

885
01:23:12.020 --> 01:23:14.955
Mummy is fine. How are you?

886
01:23:15.357 --> 01:23:16.790
Mummy will save the country

887
01:23:17.726 --> 01:23:20.957
l know you wanted custard.
But Grandma has made rice..

888
01:23:21.196 --> 01:23:22.857
..pudding with so much love. so please eat it.

889
01:23:23.098 --> 01:23:24.793
What have you brought?
Rice pudding or custard?

890
01:23:25.200 --> 01:23:28.692
We've checked the list of officers
coming from Kashmir.

891
01:23:29.037 --> 01:23:31.870
How can it not be ok?
l have hand-picked these officers.

892
01:23:32.640 --> 01:23:35.973
They are the army's very best. elite forces.

893
01:23:36.945 --> 01:23:37.809
Ok. so that's where he is.

894
01:23:38.013 --> 01:23:38.672
Who?

895
01:23:38.880 --> 01:23:40.814
An ace officer from the Jat Regiment Sir.
Captain Ranjeev.

896
01:23:41.049 --> 01:23:45.543
His wife reported he hadn't called her
for a couple of months.

897
01:23:46.421 --> 01:23:49.356
She wanted to know if he was
on some secret mission.

898
01:23:49.591 --> 01:23:54.858
That's wives for you. Am sure she was
after him with some pudding or such.

899
01:23:55.430 --> 01:23:56.522
Poor man must have needed a break from..

900
01:23:56.765 --> 01:23:58.027
..all that so he didn't call. understandable.

901
01:23:58.266 --> 01:24:00.632
He didn't call his wife for two months?
Just find out.

902
01:24:00.869 --> 01:24:03.531
was his last mission to do with the lKF?

903
01:24:07.709 --> 01:24:10.803
Yes Ma'am. Major Suraj's regiment
was surrounded by the lKF.

904
01:24:11.046 --> 01:24:14.311
At the last moment Captain Ranjeev's
regiment got there and saved them.

905
01:24:14.716 --> 01:24:19.517
Everyone from Captain Ranjeev's regiment
was killed. Only he survived.

906
01:24:22.857 --> 01:24:26.020
That's him! We have to stop him!

907
01:24:31.666 --> 01:24:36.535
Sounds like the base is trying to contact us.
The signal is too weak.

908
01:24:49.951 --> 01:24:52.010
lt's amazing isn't it? Such a small thing
can take so many lives.

909
01:24:52.320 --> 01:24:54.754
Our lives too. in it's defence - So?

910
01:24:55.156 --> 01:24:56.418
l'm not afraid of dying Sir.

911
01:24:56.658 --> 01:24:58.751
But it's better to kill for your country
than be killed

912
01:24:58.993 --> 01:25:02.861
You want to kill people?
Make them eat your wife's cooking!

913
01:25:35.063 --> 01:25:37.258
You are dying the death of a brave soldier.

914
01:25:38.166 --> 01:25:41.727
He who dies on the battlefield goes to heaven.
God keep you.

915
01:26:40.728 --> 01:26:42.821
Grandfather. l am not empty handed.

916
01:26:43.064 --> 01:26:47.501
Praise be to God! You don't have
just a trigger there with you.

917
01:26:47.902 --> 01:26:53.772
lt is our decades long dream.
We have sacrificed so much for.

918
01:26:54.576 --> 01:27:05.612
You must get that trigger to us now
at any cost. Kill. or be killed.

919
01:27:05.887 --> 01:27:07.946
Yes. grandfather. l will meet you in 3 hours..

920
01:27:08.223 --> 01:27:11.488
..At Shikara 1 pick up point. Goodbye.

921
01:27:11.893 --> 01:27:16.387
l was right. That was no accident.
He was in the helicopter.

922
01:27:16.998 --> 01:27:18.829
Jam all the phone lines in the area...

923
01:27:19.067 --> 01:27:22.161
..mobiles. satellite. internet. everything.

924
01:27:22.403 --> 01:27:23.665
l want a communications blackout.

925
01:27:23.905 --> 01:27:28.433
We can'tjam radio signals.
we have military operations in that area

926
01:27:29.677 --> 01:27:34.011
lf you can'tjam them. you can at least
monitor them. can't you?

927
01:27:34.916 --> 01:27:36.884
Search the entire area.

928
01:27:39.721 --> 01:27:41.052
How far is the road unit?

929
01:32:04.785 --> 01:32:12.385
No! He's still alive.
l don't care how many bodies you saw.

930
01:32:12.827 --> 01:32:15.591
l know Rehan will reach the pick up point.

931
01:32:16.731 --> 01:32:21.498
l have not given him permission to die.
He cannot die.

932
01:33:37.979 --> 01:33:41.676
Quickly. call Grandpa.
Go. Fast. Papa!

933
01:33:50.858 --> 01:33:52.348
Hand me the scissors please.

934
01:33:58.532 --> 01:33:59.794
Who is this. mom?

935
01:34:00.468 --> 01:34:03.562
Rehan.l don't know.
Go. please sit over there.

936
01:34:08.576 --> 01:34:11.067
ls he also dead like Grandma?

937
01:34:11.545 --> 01:34:13.012
Quiet! Little monkey

938
01:34:16.183 --> 01:34:19.744
His pulse is quite weak.
Try the phone. ls it working now?

939
01:34:23.524 --> 01:34:24.957
No papa. lt's still dead.

940
01:34:26.527 --> 01:34:29.963
We've done the best we could.
l'm no doctor.

941
01:34:30.865 --> 01:34:31.797
What can we do?

942
01:34:32.033 --> 01:34:35.298
You can't go and get a doctor in this weather.

943
01:34:35.536 --> 01:34:38.801
Not 50 kilometers in this storm.
No way.

944
01:34:39.040 --> 01:34:41.804
Mom! Please leave Rehan.

945
01:34:45.379 --> 01:34:46.812
Nothing darling. Nothing

946
01:34:49.216 --> 01:34:50.683
Now it's up to you young man.

947
01:34:52.420 --> 01:34:57.323
We can only pray you have
some reason to live.

948
01:35:02.096 --> 01:35:03.961
lt can be two days?
lt can be two weeks?

949
01:35:04.532 --> 01:35:07.126
How can you not know when
the storm will pass?

950
01:35:08.035 --> 01:35:10.799
l want an update every hour. you hear?

951
01:35:11.205 --> 01:35:12.729
Can't you do anything right?

952
01:35:16.377 --> 01:35:21.974
Till l don't see a body
l can't believe he's dead.

953
01:35:34.595 --> 01:35:37.257
Don't do that Rehan.
What are you up to?

954
01:35:37.765 --> 01:35:40.063
l can't hear his heartbeat.
There is no heartbeat.

955
01:35:40.301 --> 01:35:44.362
Rehan wants to hear his heartbeat.
like he hears Grandpa's.

956
01:35:47.942 --> 01:35:50.536
The heart is not here. it's there.

957
01:36:28.616 --> 01:36:32.518
Forgive me Zooni. l have no choice.

958
01:38:32.506 --> 01:38:34.337
Do you know the cricketer Rahul Dravid?

959
01:38:40.247 --> 01:38:42.772
Rahul Dravid is Rehan's father.

960
01:38:45.619 --> 01:38:47.553
Because Rehan's father is dead you see.

961
01:38:47.788 --> 01:38:53.886
..so mom said Rehan could choose any father.
So Rehan chose Rahul Dravid.

962
01:38:57.798 --> 01:39:00.824
Are you Mr. Dependiddle like Rahul Dravid?

963
01:39:10.311 --> 01:39:13.337
Can you also be completely
trusted like Rahul Dravid?

964
01:39:16.450 --> 01:39:18.213
That outhouse of yours is falling apart.

965
01:39:18.485 --> 01:39:21.147
Look. look the dead man is awake.

966
01:39:22.656 --> 01:39:23.987
Don't talk like that.

967
01:39:24.925 --> 01:39:31.387
When the weather is better
we'll get it fixed. lt's freezing.

968
01:39:35.402 --> 01:39:39.133
Before you thank me.
Come and eat something.

969
01:40:07.234 --> 01:40:10.362
Don't drink so much
you'll become a hittototomas.

970
01:40:11.038 --> 01:40:18.604
Not hittototomas. kid. Hippopotomas.
And where did you learn this word?

971
01:40:19.346 --> 01:40:23.077
From Colonel uncle.
Hitto. Hittototomas.

972
01:40:29.189 --> 01:40:31.919
Would you like something?
l'm sorry l didn't get your name.

973
01:40:38.265 --> 01:40:41.029
l didn't know there were military
operations here.

974
01:40:41.668 --> 01:40:45.399
There are such few of us here.
What will the militants do here?

975
01:40:46.473 --> 01:40:48.031
They can hide.

976
01:40:52.613 --> 01:40:57.141
The dead man stinks so Rehan thought..

977
01:41:00.621 --> 01:41:05.888
Strange. when Zooni couldn't see
she didn't bang into a thing.

978
01:41:07.027 --> 01:41:11.930
And now that she can see.
she's constantly walking into things.

979
