that you will forgive me.

1210
02:08:47.820 --> 02:08:50.914
l would not have left my Nafisa for anything.

1211
02:08:52.357 --> 02:08:55.724
God came in the way otherwise
l would've still been with her.

1212
02:08:57.529 --> 02:09:02.899
There is no reason to believe him.
but there is also no reason not to.

1213
02:09:04.136 --> 02:09:08.334
lt was your decision then Zooni
and it's your decision now.

1214
02:09:35.334 --> 02:09:43.742
7 years! 7 years l have lived with the guilt
that l sent you to your death.

1215
02:09:46.845 --> 02:09:52.579
Every day l curse my self for
sending you there.

1216
02:09:55.320 --> 02:09:57.550
Do you know what it's like to live with that?

1217
02:10:04.429 --> 02:10:05.088
Look at this!

1218
02:10:07.766 --> 02:10:10.098
When you were off being a great soldier ..

1219
02:10:11.003 --> 02:10:12.994
..on your missions this is what l was doing.

1220
02:10:15.207 --> 02:10:22.409
l was taking parts of all these faces.
trying to make one face. Your face.

1221
02:10:23.215 --> 02:10:27.618
So l could have something to cry in front of.
something to show my son.

1222
02:10:27.853 --> 02:10:29.218
To tell him this is your father.

1223
02:10:30.989 --> 02:10:42.093
And now you say all those tears.
all that pain was for nothing? No!

1224
02:10:45.170 --> 02:10:48.833
Why should l open myself to pain again Rehan?
Why should l take you back?

1225
02:10:51.276 --> 02:11:00.207
Give me one good reason
why l shouldn't believe you are still dead.

1226
02:11:03.055 --> 02:11:04.215
Give me one good reason.

1227
02:11:11.430 --> 02:11:23.570
l don't have a single good reason.
They are all bad. Each and every one.

1228
02:11:59.745 --> 02:12:03.511
l was taking parts of all these faces.
trying to make one face.

1229
02:12:32.945 --> 02:12:34.503
Why are you going?

1230
02:12:46.525 --> 02:12:49.619
Because l can't play cricket like Rahul Dravid.

1231
02:12:49.861 --> 02:12:53.592
Don't worry. Rehan will teach you.

1232
02:12:57.636 --> 02:13:02.437
l am not dependiddle either.
l can't be trusted.

1233
02:13:02.674 --> 02:13:09.238
No you are dependable for Rehan.
See Rehan has learned how to say dependable.

1234
02:13:09.715 --> 02:13:12.980
Rehan will never trouble you again.

1235
02:13:13.919 --> 02:13:17.821
He won't call you dead man.
He will have a bath himself.

1236
02:13:18.090 --> 02:13:22.652
He will not give you milk and turmeric.
but please don't go.

1237
02:13:35.807 --> 02:13:40.403
Rehan loves you more than you love Rehan.

1238
02:14:09.341 --> 02:14:10.205
Sit properly!

1239
02:14:12.577 --> 02:14:13.168
Eat!

1240
02:14:13.812 --> 02:14:15.507
Why are you venting your anger on him?

1241
02:14:17.115 --> 02:14:20.744
The one who deserves it has left
without saying a word.

1242
02:14:23.188 --> 02:14:26.817
He must be in his room.
Go tell him breakfast is ready.

1243
02:14:27.059 --> 02:14:29.459
l'm not going to stand around
in the kitchen all day for him.

1244
02:14:29.761 --> 02:14:32.730
He's gone. He said goodbye to Rehan.
Not to you.

1245
02:14:41.706 --> 02:14:49.374
No. he can't go. He can't go.

1246
02:15:19.444 --> 02:15:21.173
How dare you leave me again.
How dare you?

1247
02:15:21.713 --> 02:15:30.417
Your life is mine now. do you hear?
You can never leave me and go. Never!

1248
02:16:00.218 --> 02:16:00.809
Papa!

1249
02:16:01.086 --> 02:16:05.887
When l have your hands in mine.

1250
02:16:06.124 --> 02:16:11.061
l have with me the heavens divine.

1251
02:16:11.296 --> 02:16:16.165
When l have your hands in mine.

1252
02:16:16.401 --> 02:16:21.338
l have with me the heavens divine.

1253
02:16:21.606 --> 02:16:26.509
When you're close. this world is naught.

1254
02:16:26.745 --> 02:16:31.478
Destroyed in your love. a triumph sought.

1255
02:16:31.783 --> 02:16:36.584
When l have your hands in mine.

1256
02:16:36.821 --> 02:16:41.758
l have with me the heavens divine.

1257
02:16:42.027 --> 02:16:46.862
When you're close this world is naught.

1258
02:16:47.098 --> 02:16:51.967
Destroyed in your love. a triumph sought.

1259
02:16:52.204 --> 02:16:57.039
When l have your hands in mine.

1260
02:16:57.275 --> 02:17:02.406
l have with me the heavens divine.

1261
02:17:25.170 --> 02:17:27.934
May my life's-breath find refuge in your heart.

1262
02:17:29.074 --> 02:17:32.271
Destroyed in your love may my life depart.

1263
02:17:33.078 --> 02:17:37.947
As close as fragrances are to breath.

1264
02:17:38.183 --> 02:17:43.052
As close as songs are to lips.

1265
02:17:43.288 --> 02:17:48.191
As close as sleepless nights to memories.

1266
02:17:48.426 --> 02:17:52.795
As close as arms are to embraces.

1267
02:17:53.465 --> 02:17:58.528
As close. as close as dreams to eyes.

1268
02:17:58.770 --> 02:18:02.604
Be that close to me. oh love of mine.

1269
02:18:03.842 --> 02:18:08.609
When you're close this world is naught.

1270
02:18:08.847 --> 02:18:13.580
Destroyed in your love. a triumph sought.

1271
02:18:13.918 --> 02:18:18.787
When l have your hands in mine.

1272
02:18:19.024 --> 02:18:24.223
l have with me the heavens divine.

1273
02:18:45.583 --> 02:18:49.849
Let my eyes swell with tears. let me cry today.

1274
02:18:50.689 --> 02:18:53.749
Take me in your arms. get drenched today.

1275
02:18:55.160 --> 02:18:59.756
The sea of pain trapped in my heart will explode.

1276
02:19:00.432 --> 02:19:04.562
l have so much pain your veil will be drenched.

1277
02:19:05.036 --> 02:19:09.973
As close as secrets are to heartbeats.

1278
02:19:10.208 --> 02:19:14.941
As close as raindrops are to clouds.

1279
02:19:15.180 --> 02:19:20.049
As close as the moon is to night.

1280
02:19:20.318 --> 02:19:24.755
As close as kohl is to eyes.

1281
02:19:25.490 --> 02:19:30.553
As close. as close as waves to the ocean.

1282
02:19:30.795 --> 02:19:35.459
Be that close to me. oh love of mine.

1283
02:19:35.800 --> 02:19:40.669
When you're close this world is naught.

1284
02:19:40.905 --> 02:19:45.569
Destroyed in your love. a triumph sought.

1285
02:19:45.910 --> 02:19:50.904
When l have your hands in mine.

1286
02:19:51.149 --> 02:19:56.018
l have with me the heavens divine.

1287
02:19:57.188 --> 02:20:02.592
My breath was incomplete. heartbeat incomplete.
incomplete was l.

1288
02:20:03.361 --> 02:20:05.022
But now the moon is full. complete in the sky.
and now with you complete am l..

1289
02:20:30.822 --> 02:20:33.814
Give us some good news Aakash.
Can we go any further?

1290
02:20:34.092 --> 02:20:36.185
Sorry ma'am. we'll have to wait
another 2 or 3 days.

1291
02:20:36.428 --> 02:20:40.524
But we have to do something Aakash.
We can't just stand around.

1292
02:20:43.168 --> 02:20:47.366
No. Not the press. We can't talk to the
media about the bomb yet.

1293
02:20:47.839 --> 02:20:49.704
The order's come directly from Delhi.

1294
02:20:49.941 --> 02:20:54.207
We can't talk about the bomb
but we can talk about him.

1295
02:20:54.946 --> 02:21:00.316
Aakash! lnform the press.
Newspaper. Radio. TV.

1296
02:21:00.919 --> 02:21:03.854
The search is on for a terrorist
hiding in the outskirts of Srinagar.

1297
02:21:04.088 --> 02:21:07.990
This terrorist is badly wounded
and is wearing an army uniform.

1298
02:21:08.259 --> 02:21:10.352
He is also carrying an electronic part.

1299
02:21:10.595 --> 02:21:15.191
lf you have any information
on this man please..

1300
02:21:15.433 --> 02:21:18.368
..contact your nearest police station immediately.

1301
02:21:23.174 --> 02:21:24.539
Come on Rehan. drink your milk.

1302
02:21:26.845 --> 02:21:31.043
Rehan loves you more than you love Rehan.

1303
02:21:31.449 --> 02:21:37.547
No. l love Rehan much more than that
and he has to drink this milk.

1304
02:21:37.822 --> 02:21:38.754
And what about this Rehan?

1305
02:21:44.496 --> 02:21:45.428
At this time?

1306
02:21:51.503 --> 02:21:53.266
Colonel? At this time?
What's the matter?

1307
02:21:53.505 --> 02:21:57.100
l have risked life and come here
for a very important reason.

1308
02:22:00.311 --> 02:22:01.903
l've run out of rum!

1309
02:22:03.448 --> 02:22:08.545
The games destiny plays with us.
And if one is in the army their..

1310
02:22:09.487 --> 02:22:11.921
..destiny is not in their hands anyway. Cheers!

1311
02:22:16.828 --> 02:22:22.095
Rehan. if you like you can come
to my house and radio your unit.

1312
02:22:22.500 --> 02:22:24.092
You have a radio transmitter?

1313
02:22:24.903 --> 02:22:27.269
Meet the man who lives
in the middle of nowhere..

1314
02:22:27.505 --> 02:22:30.269
..and keeps a radio to keep in touch with people.

1315
02:22:30.508 --> 02:22:33.773
Always wonder why he lives out here.

1316
02:22:34.512 --> 02:22:37.777
lt's late today. lt'll be dark
by the time you return.

1317
02:22:38.016 --> 02:22:38.778
lt's dark already.

1318
02:22:39.017 --> 02:22:40.609
Ok. so it's night already.
Come tomorrow. The weather..

1319
02:22:40.885 --> 02:22:44.150
..should be clearer as well.
Come and radio your unit then.

1320
02:22:44.389 --> 02:22:45.822
There's no need for that.

1321
02:22:46.057 --> 02:22:46.819
Why not?

1322
02:22:47.058 --> 02:22:47.820
He has just returned after 7 years.
l don't want..

1323
02:22:48.059 --> 02:22:49.822
..him to disappear for another 7.

1324
02:22:50.295 --> 02:22:55.164
You are trying to guard a soldier is it?
Rehan. do you want me to radio them?

1325
02:22:55.567 --> 02:22:57.330
No. l'll have to do it myself.

1326
02:22:58.403 --> 02:22:59.165
Of course. of course.

1327
02:22:59.404 --> 02:23:01.429
Let him give his status report then you..

1328
02:23:01.673 --> 02:23:05.609
..can keep him imprisoned here
forever. right Rehan?

1329
02:23:06.177 --> 02:23:08.611
Fine. now no more discussion.
What do they say in Punjabi?

1330
02:23:08.913 --> 02:23:10.608
Let's have a whopper of a drink.

1331
02:23:45.917 --> 02:23:50.183
Where's your father?
He was to take me to colonels' house.

1332
02:23:52.457 --> 02:23:53.719
Do you really have to go?

1333
02:23:56.461 --> 02:23:57.894
Just this last bit of work.

1334
02:24:00.398 --> 02:24:04.835
Papa takes a while to get ready.
He'll be down soon. Papa!

1335
02:24:17.415 --> 02:24:21.351
Once upon a time there was a prince.
and a princess who was blind.

1336
02:24:21.619 --> 02:24:23.177
Mom. you are telling a story?

1337
02:24:25.790 --> 02:24:28.384
One day the princess
met an ordinary man who..

1338
02:24:28.626 --> 02:24:32.562
..followed different monuments
in different cities.

1339
02:24:33.464 --> 02:24:37.730
But the princess saw the prince
hidden in that ordinary man.

1340
02:24:38.636 --> 02:24:40.399
What was the prince's name?

1341
02:24:41.305 --> 02:24:41.896
Rehan.

1342
02:24:52.150 --> 02:24:56.086
The prince saved the princess
from a huge. scary dragon.

1343
02:24:57.021 --> 02:25:01.856
The dragon had a big. red face.
Every time he opened his mouth..

1344
02:25:02.126 --> 02:25:04.720
..gigantic balls of fire would come out of it.

1345
02:25:04.962 --> 02:25:06.395
What was the dragon's name?

1346
02:25:08.466 --> 02:25:09.728
Grandpa!

1347
02:25:12.470 --> 02:25:17.567
Come on Rehan. let's go to the
Colonel's and radio your unit.

1348
02:25:18.643 --> 02:25:21.237
The search is on for a terrorist hiding
in the outskirts of Srinagar.

1349
02:25:21.479 --> 02:25:23.743
This terrorist is wearing an army uniform.

1350
02:25:23.981 --> 02:25:25.915
He is also carrying an electronic part.

1351
02:25:31.689 --> 02:25:35.090
Grandpa. Rehan loves you very much.

1352
02:25:49.707 --> 02:25:53.643
l will have to go for a couple of days
to hand in my resignation.

1353
02:25:54.545 --> 02:25:59.312
Whether or not you're on this mission.
the lKF will definitely loose.

1354
02:26:00.084 --> 02:26:01.949
Terrorists can never win.

1355
02:26:02.687 --> 02:26:06.453
That's the thing. These people are not terrorists.
They are fighting for their independence.

1356
02:26:07.425 --> 02:26:10.292
And who will run this country of theirs?
The lKF?

1357
02:26:10.695 --> 02:26:15.291
No. Whoever the people of Kashmir elect.
ln fair elections.

1358
02:26:16.367 --> 02:26:20.804
lt seems you're not against the lKF.
you're for of them.

1359
02:26:45.763 --> 02:26:49.358
You are a traitor.
You may be my daughter's husband.

1360
02:26:49.767 --> 02:26:52.201
..but l'll gladly kill you.

1361
02:26:52.770 --> 02:26:57.366
l was doubtful when l saw the news on the TV.
but by then it was too late.

1362
02:26:59.610 --> 02:27:03.637
l had my doubts. But today l was certain..

1363
02:27:03.881 --> 02:27:07.647
..when l found this trigger in your pocket.

1364
02:27:10.087 --> 02:27:13.488
You can't do anything now.
l am going to radio the..

1365
02:27:13.758 --> 02:27:19.025
..military and hand you over.
Colonel! Colonel!

1366
02:27:21.165 --> 02:27:25.033
Please sir. give me that trigger.
All this will be over in a couple of days.

1367
02:27:25.269 --> 02:27:27.362
Then l can stay with Zooni
and Rehan forever.

1368
02:27:27.605 --> 02:27:30.369
l'd rather they be dead.
l'll never give you this. Never.

1369
02:27:42.820 --> 02:27:44.754
Don't you dare. Rehan!

1370
02:27:46.324 --> 02:27:47.757
No!!

1371
02:27:53.998 --> 02:27:57.764
No!!

1372
02:28:20.992 --> 02:28:26.259
My son. Rehan!
God be praised a million times.

1373
02:28:26.497 --> 02:28:30.934
You're alive! Do you have what l want?

1374
02:28:32.169 --> 02:28:34.103
Yes. l have it with me.

1375
02:28:34.372 --> 02:28:35.430
What's the matter?

1376
02:28:35.840 --> 02:28:40.777
l'm tired that's all.
l just want all this to end.

1377
02:28:41.012 --> 02:28:41.444
Look here..

1378
02:28:41.679 --> 02:28:45.775
l know what l have to do.
Come here and take what it is you want.

1379
02:28:47.551 --> 02:28:52.955
The coordinates here are loc rep 34.7 4...

1380
02:28:54.558 --> 02:28:56.992
..mount 2730. 500 house.

1381
02:28:59.063 --> 02:29:03.261
That was him. Thank God
he hasn't reached his people yet.

1382
02:29:03.501 --> 02:29:06.265
There is very heavy fog right now. We'll try and be..

1383
02:29:07.238 --> 02:29:11.766
..there tomorrow morning.
God be with you.

1384
02:29:23.888 --> 02:29:27.790
Sorry ma'am he gave his location in code.
We'll need some time to break it.

1385
02:29:30.294 --> 02:29:31.818
Give Ranade the code to break.

1386
02:29:32.063 --> 02:29:33.496
Keep the ground search going.

1387
02:29:33.731 --> 02:29:35.392
And continue monitoring the
frequency he called from.

1388
02:29:37.735 --> 02:29:41.330
We only have till tomorrow morning.
Contact the base camp.

1389
02:29:41.572 --> 02:29:43.665
Are they ready with the sketch of the
imposter of Captain Ranjeev?

1390
02:30:04.795 --> 02:30:07.059
Papa!!

1391
02:30:12.970 --> 02:30:16.064
Papa! Someone help us please!

1392
02:30:24.482 --> 02:30:26.416
Mom. what's happened?

1393
02:30:31.022 --> 02:30:34.423
Papa! Papa!

1394
02:30:53.878 --> 02:30:55.140
Mom! What happened?

1395
02:30:57.381 --> 02:31:00.407
Nothing. go watch some TV.

1396
02:31:03.687 --> 02:31:05.621
Rehan. Papa...

1397
02:31:05.856 --> 02:31:09.622
l've just left him at Colonel uncle's.
They're both drinking rum.

1398
02:31:12.029 --> 02:31:14.964
He said he'll stay there tonight.

1399
02:31:18.035 --> 02:31:21.801
The search is on for a terrorist
hiding in the outskirts of Srinagar.

1400
02:31:22.039 --> 02:31:26.305
This terrorist is badly wounded
and is wearing an army uniform.

1401
02:31:26.544 --> 02:31:29.479
He went missing 8 days ago.

1402
02:31:29.713 --> 02:31:31.806
He has an electronic part with him.

1403
02:31:32.049 --> 02:31:34.643
This is a sketch of him provided by the army.

1404
02:31:34.919 --> 02:31:38.480
lf you see this man anywhere
please don't try and catch him your self.

1405
02:31:38.756 --> 02:31:39.814
He is armed and dangerous.

1406
02:31:40.091 --> 02:31:42.525
Please contact your nearest police..

1407
02:31:42.760 --> 02:31:45.024
..station immediately.
Or call this number.

1408
02:34:04.335 --> 02:34:07.930
Hello! Hello! Can someone hear me?

1409
02:34:08.339 --> 02:34:10.432
Ma'am someone is sending an
SOS from the same frequency.

1410
02:34:10.674 --> 02:34:12.767
Hello. Hello. Yes we read you.

1411
02:34:13.010 --> 02:34:17.037
Hello. can someone hear me?

1412
02:34:17.281 --> 02:34:18.509
Hello. yes. we can hear you.

1413
02:34:18.749 --> 02:34:23.311
l am Malini Tyagi from the
anti terrorist special forces. Who is this?

1414
02:34:24.555 --> 02:34:32.155
l am Zooni Ali Beg. My husband.
l thought he was dead.

1415
02:34:32.663 --> 02:34:38.624
But he came back 9 days ago.
l think he's the one you are looking for.

1416
02:34:40.738 --> 02:34:45.675
He may have killed my father
and my uncle. Or not.

1417
02:34:46.610 --> 02:34:54.210
l don't know. Just please help us.
l am alone. lt's just me and my son.

1418
02:34:54.485 --> 02:34:58.285
Zooni. Zooni don't panic.
And listen to me carefully.

1419
02:34:58.956 --> 02:35:02.050
Does your husband have
some sort of an electronic part?

1420
02:35:02.293 --> 02:35:10.928
Yes. l saw it on TV. lt's with me.

1421
02:35:11.568 --> 02:35:18.667
lt's him. Your husband is the one
we are looking for. He is the terrorist.

1422
02:35:23.947 --> 02:35:28.247
Listen to me carefully Zooni.
l am going to tell you the most..

1423
02:35:28.519 --> 02:35:31.317
..important thing you will ever hear.
lf he leaves with that trigger.

1424
02:35:31.555 --> 02:35:34.046
..if he joins his comrades they will..

1425
02:35:34.525 --> 02:35:38.825
..use a nuclear bomb over our country.

1426
02:35:39.129 --> 02:35:41.359
Millions of lndians will die.

1427
02:35:42.333 --> 02:35:47.828
One of them can be my daughter.
Another can be your son.

1428
02:35:49.306 --> 02:35:50.773
There will be complete destruction...

1429
02:35:51.075 --> 02:35:56.411
..and the only one who can
stop it Zooni. is you!

1430
02:35:58.382 --> 02:36:02.443
But. he is my husband.

1431
02:36:02.720 --> 02:36:05.052
Tell me you will help us Zooni.

1432
02:36:06.490 --> 02:36:11.120
Tell me you will stop him.
Whatever it takes.

1433
02:36:14.064 --> 02:36:14.723
Yes.

1434
02:36:16.800 --> 02:36:19.735
We have your location now Zooni.

1435
02:36:20.037 --> 02:36:21.368
We know where you are...

1436
02:36:22.072 --> 02:36:23.733
...we'll be there tomorrow morning.

1437
02:36:23.974 --> 02:36:24.838
Ok.

1438
02:37:21.198 --> 02:37:28.331
Who are you running away from?
From me? From your Rehan?

1439
02:37:29.773 --> 02:37:33.709
l have only one Rehan. My son.

1440
02:37:37.147 --> 02:37:39.240
Papa? What happened?

1441
02:37:41.351 --> 02:37:43.819
Nothing son. Everything is fine.

1442
02:37:50.027 --> 02:37:54.020
What's the point?
You'll kill him as well.

1443
02:37:56.366 --> 02:37:57.833
l'd rather die first.

1444
02:37:58.435 --> 02:38:00.528
You killed Papa quite easily.

1445
02:38:05.476 --> 02:38:10.641
l didn't kill him.
lt was an accident.

1446
02:38:14.117 --> 02:38:15.345
And Colonel Uncle?

1447
02:38:27.197 --> 02:38:28.824
Give me the trigger Zooni.

1448
02:38:29.933 --> 02:38:30.797
No.

1449
02:38:35.606 --> 02:38:36.971
Give me that trigger!

1450
02:38:38.942 --> 02:38:43.743
What will you do?
Kill me as well? Kill me.

1451
02:38:44.381 --> 02:38:48.784
l've already died once because of you.
why not once again.

1452
02:38:51.221 --> 02:38:54.816
Zooni. despite all my lies.

1453
02:38:56.059 --> 02:38:58.254
Despite all the pain l have given you.

1454
02:38:59.563 --> 02:39:04.626
Do you believe that l love you?

1455
02:39:08.171 --> 02:39:09.399
Then for the sake of that love.

1456
02:39:10.707 --> 02:39:15.440
You have to do what l say.
lf you don't give me that trigger..

1457
02:39:16.146 --> 02:39:19.809
..then they will torture and
kill Rehan right in front of us.

1458
02:39:21.418 --> 02:39:22.942
Then they'll kill you in front of me.

1459
02:39:24.254 --> 02:39:28.088
Then if they have any mercy.
then they will kill me too

1460
02:39:30.060 --> 02:39:32.494
And the person to do all this
will be no stranger.

1461
02:39:33.597 --> 02:39:38.466
My own grandfather will destroy
his family with his own hands.

1462
02:39:40.571 --> 02:39:42.061
l don't care about myself Zooni.

1463
02:39:43.206 --> 02:39:45.902
but l am not willing to
sacrifice Rehan or you.

1464
02:39:49.513 --> 02:40:00.390
This is the only way we'll be able to
live our lives in peace again.

1465
02:40:04.094 --> 02:40:07.461
And what about the lives of those millions
that will die from the bomb?

1466
02:40:07.965 --> 02:40:12.959
No one will use the bomb. lt's just a threat.
The governments..

1467
02:40:13.203 --> 02:40:15.433
..of lndia and Pakistan will have
no other choice. but to give in.

1468
02:40:21.979 --> 02:40:27.178
After all your lies. how can l believe you now?

1469
02:40:32.122 --> 02:40:33.180
Grandfather

1470
02:40:35.325 --> 02:40:39.591
Or the lndian army whom l called.

1471
02:40:50.374 --> 02:40:52.706
No. Grandfather.

1472
02:40:56.713 --> 02:41:00.080
You can't leave.

1473
02:41:05.455 --> 02:41:12.156
Take care of Rehan and yourself.
l'll be back tomorrow.

1474
02:41:32.883 --> 02:41:40.312
Rehan! Please for our son's sake. Stop!

1475
02:43:38.508 --> 02:43:40.533
Why Rehan? Why?

1476
02:43:46.516 --> 02:43:51.215
Rehan loves you more than you love Rehan.

1477
02:43:51.521 --> 02:43:55.753
Don't say that. Please don't.

1478
02:44:06.102 --> 02:44:10.562
Now l'm not scared.

1479
02:44:38.568 --> 02:44:43.369
When l have your hands in mine

1480
02:44:43.607 --> 02:44:48.510
l have with me heavens divine

1481
02:44:48.745 --> 02:44:53.648
When l have your hands in mine

1482
02:44:53.917 --> 02:44:58.786
l have with me heavens divine

1483
02:44:59.022 --> 02:45:03.857
When you're close this world is naught

1484
02:45:04.094 --> 02:45:08.758
Destroyed in your love. a triumph sought

1485
02:45:09.666 --> 02:45:12.931
lt's easy to choose
between right and wrong.

1486
02:45:13.870 --> 02:45:16.532
But to choose the greater of two goods..

1487
02:45:16.773 --> 02:45:23.144
..or the lesser of two evils.
Those are the choices of our life.

1488
02:45:30.787 --> 02:45:33.051
Rehan loves you very much

1489
02:45:36.760 --> 02:45:39.285
And Zooni loves Rehan very much.
